    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの提案で、星見プロからみんなに\n誕生日プレゼントとして慰安旅行を計画したんだ",
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "startTime": 17.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？",
      "startTime": 20.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "startTime": 21.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\nえっ？",
      "startTime": 22.4333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ？",
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4282.053164500003,
          "startTime": 29.1487198312
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ誕生日慰安旅行in京都",
      "startTime": 27.2153867522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "イベリコ豚とロースステーキ重……\nふわふわのたまごサンドに、シュウマイ弁当……",
      "startTime": 33.8820517658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "美味しそうな駅弁を諦めたのに\n高級料亭の予約が取れていなかったなんて……",
      "startTime": 41.2153850991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私、もうお腹ペコペコですわ～",
      "startTime": 45.3820539273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、すずちゃん。{user}さんが今\n別のお店に電話してくれてるから……",
      "startTime": 55.0487184325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんから慌てて電話がかかってきた時は\nどうなるかと思いましたが、なんとかなりそうですね",
      "startTime": 61.2820510029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。京都出身の優が\n知り合いの料亭を紹介してくれて助かったわ",
      "startTime": 68.3153850991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが紹介してくれた料亭だから\n凄く美味しいんだろうなあ……",
      "startTime": 74.6623766883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、キャビアに、フォアグラ……\nフカヒレも、ある……",
      "startTime": 79.7518882621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あまり京料理らしくない食材ばかりですが……\nそこまで素晴らしい料亭なら待つほかありませんわね！",
      "startTime": 85.8153850991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "夜泊まる旅館も、優ちゃんのオススメの旅館なんだよね",
      "startTime": 90.0487170337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。嵐山の紅葉が部屋から楽しめる\n百五十年続く人気の老舗旅館らしいわ",
      "startTime": 98.8487184325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "温泉もあるみたいだから\n夜はゆっくり日頃の疲れを癒せそうね",
      "startTime": 104.1820517658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんで京都なんですの？\n私はハワイとかロサンゼルスを希望しましたのよ",
      "startTime": 110.5820517658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ贅沢だよ、すずちゃん\n京都は、私とお姉ちゃんでリクエストしたんだ",
      "startTime": 118.6820517658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。私は京都の寺社仏閣を見たくて……\n千紗は、京都のパワースポットに興味があるのよね",
      "startTime": 127.0153850991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "パワースポットもだけど\n心霊スポットも沢山あるみたいなの！",
      "startTime": 132.9487184325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "し、心霊スポット……！？　怖いですわ……\n変なもの連れて帰ったら許しませんわ！",
      "startTime": 141.6153769611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに京都は歴史も長く様々な伝承が残っていますから\nそういった場所があるのも不思議ではありません",
      "startTime": 150.2820436278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんも、京都に行く直前に\n突然熱を出して倒れたし……",
      "startTime": 156.5820436278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ひー！\nや、やはり関係あるんですの！？",
      "startTime": 160.7820507485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "すず、落ち着いて。関係あるはずないでしょう",
      "startTime": 164.9153745451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
